{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>It's time you learnt how to play.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>GAME</i> follows the story of a champion player of a cryptic and bizarre sport set in a vibrant and surreal world. Awoken at dawn one morning by your mother and shown the basics, you are thereafter thrust onto the path towards stardom\u2014whether you like it or not.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Told through a series of scenes and conversations spread throughout your life, equal parts funny and sad, <i>GAME </i>spans several decades and a wide variety of colorful and evocative locations. The dialogue choices you make with the people you meet along the way will impact the  path you take, and the ultimate conclusion to your story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Approx 2 hours for one playthrough, depending on the path you take</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple paths and outcomes influenced by your dialogue choices throughout the game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bizarre and beautiful locations rendered in colorful, stylized 3D artwork</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A choral russian folk soundtrack to rival any Werner Herzog documentary</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400310/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736246219","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400310/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736246219","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400310/4c09e8914d181255d82e076c2e06c26f6e090900/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736246219","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400310/4c09e8914d181255d82e076c2e06c26f6e090900/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736246219","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"conten